-- Add new Layer 2 ecosystems and connect them to Ethereum

-- Add Optimism Layer 2
ecoadd Optimism
repadd Optimism https://github.com/ethereum-optimism/optimism #protocol
repadd Optimism https://github.com/ethereum-optimism/optimism-tutorial #developer-tool
repadd Optimism https://github.com/ethereum-optimism/optimism-wallet #wallet

-- Add Arbitrum Layer 2
ecoadd Arbitrum
repadd Arbitrum https://github.com/OffchainLabs/arbitrum #protocol
repadd Arbitrum https://github.com/OffchainLabs/arbitrum-sdk #developer-tool
repadd Arbitrum https://github.com/OffchainLabs/arbitrum-wallet #wallet

-- Add Polygon Layer 2
ecoadd Polygon
repadd Polygon https://github.com/maticnetwork/polygon-sdk #protocol
repadd Polygon https://github.com/maticnetwork/polygon-js-sdk #developer-tool
repadd Polygon https://github.com/maticnetwork/polygon-wallet #wallet

-- Add Base Layer 2
ecoadd Base
repadd Base https://github.com/base-org/base-contracts #protocol
repadd Base https://github.com/base-org/base-sdk #developer-tool
repadd Base https://github.com/base-org/base-wallet #wallet

-- Connect all Layer 2s to Ethereum as parent ecosystem
ecocon Ethereum Optimism
ecocon Ethereum Arbitrum
ecocon Ethereum Polygon
ecocon Ethereum Base

-- Connect TestChain to Ethereum as well
ecocon Ethereum TestChain
